<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.3">
<l>āṉaip puravi tēro ṭukālā ḷaṇikoṇṭa</l>
<l>cēṉait tokaiyaic cāṭi yilaṅkai ceṟṟāṉūr</l>
<l>mīṉait taḻuvi vīḻnte ḻumaḷḷark kalamantu</l>
<l>nāṉap putali lāmai yoḷikkum naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the one who destroyed Laṅkā, trampling its army troops</l>
<l>Which had divisions of elephants, horses, chariots, and foot soldiers,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr where turtles hide in the fragrant bushes, fearing powerful men</l>
<l>Who, plunging [in a pool and] having caught fish, rise [up out of the water].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
